rows.label: qst104702_msg001
rows.name:
That ship is carrying refugees
from Superbia. They say it's
heading to Gula from here.

rows.label: qst104702_msg002
rows.name:
I hear they have an escort,
but things have been so
dangerous lately, I'm worried.

rows.label: qst104702_msg003
rows.name:
You there. If you don't mind, could
you go to Gula and check on them?

rows.label: qst104702_msg0001
rows.name:
The ship from Superbia
has not arrived...

rows.label: qst104702_msg0002
rows.name:
It is long past its
scheduled arrival time...

rows.label: qst104702_msg0003
rows.name:
It was supposed to resupply at
Yeshiva Harbor in Liberalitas. Has
it even arrived there, I wonder...

rows.label: qst104702_msg0004
rows.name:
Could you check for me? That
would be a great help!

rows.label: qst104702_msg0005
rows.name:
It would be fine if it
were merely a delay...

rows.label: qst104702_msg0101
rows.name:
The number of people leaving
the Imperial Capital has
been increasing lately.

rows.label: qst104702_msg0102
rows.name:
I have a slight concern about
whether we can accommodate all of
their citizens in the future...
